Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.11,0:46:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,that out. And they'll have you licking\Ntheir boots thinking you're serving God.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.40,0:46:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,All right? I don't want to build them up\Nto greater be greater than what they
