Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.07,0:47:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No. So, we've seen them crash and burn\None after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.11,0:47:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we're innocent, we believe in\Npurity and goodness and all these kind
