Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.92,0:49:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,know I'm saying strange you know\Ntotally unexpected out of the blue
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.76,0:49:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,we all know that spiritual wisdom says\Nleave Ouija boards alone
