Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.72,0:58:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean a very advanced state at one time\Nbeyond all form
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.72,0:58:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,in a state of infinite power.\NUm,
