Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.88,1:00:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,was like a very high pass. I saw who had\Nbeen through there and I saw the answer
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.72,1:00:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,they had given.\NAnd the defect was to try to own the
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.59,1:00:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,power of God\Nand without owning the love of God.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.35,1:00:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,God is infinite power also infinite\Nlove. So the luciferic energy
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.92,1:00:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,tries to\Nseal the power of God but escape the
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.20,1:00:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,love of God because that would be a\Nlimitation.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.79,1:00:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't kill off millions of people if\Nyou're still capable of love. You have
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.52,1:00:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,to eliminate lovingness and now you can\Nkill them and have infinite domain over
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.48,1:00:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,them.\NAnyway, at that space,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.52,1:01:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,the knowingness\Nof this consciousness was already
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.52,1:01:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,sufficiently advanced to negate that\Ntemptation and say no to it. Can never
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.04,1:01:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,be used for personal gain.\NI saw Jesus Christ had been there and
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.52,1:01:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,said no to it. I saw some other gurus\Nthroughout history who had said yes to
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.44,1:01:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,it and I saw why they say yes. It's\Nbecause they had not had the karmic
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.83,1:01:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,um gain of having been\Neducated by their own teacher in advance
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.52,1:01:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,to know better.\NSo I feel it's my responsibility to
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.72,1:01:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,share such things\Nthat such a thing will not befall you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.20,1:01:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Because these things come\Nunannounced, unexpected. You're just
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.20,1:01:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,sitting there meditating or releasing on\Nsomething, uh, chanting, uh, maybe doing
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.07,1:01:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the Jesus prayer, walking through the\Nwoods, and all of a sudden it comes to
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.76,1:02:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,you. You got no time to think it over.\NHow am I going to answer this? How I'm
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.07,1:02:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,going to handle it? Unless you've heard\Nabout it before, and bring it right up.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.16,1:02:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll come up. It'll come up. Having\Nheard it, having heard it, it comes up
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.96,1:02:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,at the time. Having heard it, you've\Nheard it now. When that comes to you,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.64,1:02:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the knowingness arises out of beyond\Nthinkingness.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.76,1:02:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Having heard it, one is now protected.\NOne is now protected. So those that have
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.44,1:02:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,fallen,\NI feel a compassion for. They were
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.31,1:02:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,somehow unprotected.\NTheir teachers did not share with them.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.04,1:02:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe their teachers didn't know.\NAnd so they fell they fell over the
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.48,1:02:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,abyss. The way back from over the abyss\Nis hellish and can be awful and take
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.28,1:02:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,long, long periods of time, longer than\Nanybody in this audience can know what I
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.07,1:02:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,mean by long long eons of time to come\Nback from the serious fall of grace.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.59,1:03:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh so um I say this out of respect for\Nthe evolution of the consciousness of
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.44,1:03:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,everybody in this room because everybody\Nin this room has reached the point of
