Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.35,1:03:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,eaten by them.\NWhy it's inappropriate to reveal a name
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.28,1:03:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,to someone like that who would be such a\Nnegative influence all
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.96,1:03:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,>> I don't get what he's saying\N>> the the person that we were calibrating
