Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.40,1:04:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,discoveries such as I do with Susan\Nlet's say uh it's a different thing it
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.35,1:04:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,could be that there's a different\Nconsequence of speaking publicly for one
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.76,1:04:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,thing it could be\Num shocking to somebody so a lot of
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.88,1:04:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,times people will ask me what is such\Nand such a guru book calibrate I want
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.24,1:04:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,them to find out for themsel because\Nthere's there could be like a shock
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.52,1:04:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,shock\Ncould be like a shock.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.07,1:04:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I went through a shock like that one\Ntime. It was horrible.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.64,1:04:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I discovered the guru that I've been\Nfollowing the heart chakra was zero. He
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.24,1:04:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,had zero energy in the heart chakra.\NSuddenly everything that he'd said took
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.72,1:04:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,on a whole different context.\NSo all right. Um
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.44,1:04:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,we are preparing a book where we're\Ngoing to do a thousand calibrations and
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.03,1:05:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,again it's iffy. We have to ask\Nconstantly ask should we share this? Can
