Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.92,1:05:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,right through society like the grim\Nreaper. You know what I mean? And but
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.11,1:05:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,that's not the purpose. We get that the\Npurpose is merely educational.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.76,1:05:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Each of us needs to take responsibility\Nfor the evolution of our own
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.20,1:05:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness. And in so doing, we earn\Na certain karmic merit. All I want
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.72,1:05:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,people to do is to be aware. Don't be\Nnaively foolish. Fall for anything. Be
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.07,1:05:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,aware that there is a downside. Uh a\Ncertain amount of fallacy out there that
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.72,1:06:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,masquerades as the legitimate. Jesus\NChrist said the same thing. He said,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.24,1:06:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,"Beware the wolf in sheep's clothing."\NRight?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.59,1:06:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't know kinesiology.\NHe didn't tell you how said the
