Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.35,1:06:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,been by their fruits we shall know them.\NWe could say killing 3,000 innocent
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.68,1:06:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,people would indicate\Nthat this is probably not of the most
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.44,1:06:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,pure and delicate. you know,\Nuh, by their fruits we shall know them.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.79,1:06:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,All right? So, that's all we've had to\Ngo by. And by karmic merit, apparently
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.28,1:06:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,in the late 1980s,\Nwe were like given a way of telling the
