Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.60,1:09:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,the breastplate of truth as Jesus said.\NIsn't that what he said? The breastplate
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.79,1:09:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,of truth. Uh to guard one against um\Nwhat I call spiritual seduction.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.04,1:09:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual seduction. and to be aware\Nthat there are those entities within the
